headline: Nasdaq Announces Quarterly Dividend  of $0.27 Per Share
summary: NEW YORK, July 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Board of Directors of Nasdaq, Inc. (Nasdaq: NDAQ) has declared a regular quarterly dividend of $0.27 per share on the company's outstanding common stock. The dividend is payable on September 26, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on September 12, 2025.
